%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A3-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-i6J_gjKNUJ7zwhSthu0ADQ">Tả hoài kỳ 1 - 寫懷其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/T%E1%BB%AD-D%E1%BA%A1-h%E1%BA%A1-ca/poem-o-lu9mzfo2Dlz5onkAhcVA">Tử Dạ hạ ca - 子夜夏歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/V%C4%83n-th%C3%A1i-phong-l%C6%B0u/poem-PTBoGiZ0rQjiB-CvRgsN1w">Văn thái phong lưu - 文采風流</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br></div>	</div>
